ins in. Mend.. <BR>  <BR> You have worsened your wounds! (Oh sh!t...) <BR> I turn to run and get stunned twice in a row, seeing a nice panaramic view while the wisps beat my ass into the ground. <BR>  <BR> I take off running, giving some /y's. I get missed _12_ times in a row by the wisps (with 63 agility!!!) I run past the other guy, and the wisp he has near dead *aggros on ME*. So here I am, running to the EC zone, with 3 wisps, a necro, and his pet in tow. The wisps constantly are missing me, and only hitting for 1 damage. Almost to the zone, a wisp dies. The two open a can on me (Ok, so they hit me for 11 and 13) dropping me down to practically nothing. I hit my 3 hotkey (personna), and see 17 hps left as I hit the zone line. When I finish zoning, i've got 0 stamina (alot of jumping), and 6 hps. <BR>  <BR> Regretably, the 2 wisps turned and killed the necro. He got stunlocked and died very close to the zone, apparently. <BR>  <BR> Why did I not die? How could I run 1/4th of the zone with 1/2 a bubble of hps? <BR>  <BR> A druid was hunting guards at the tollbooth, so he sow'd everyone there. Since the guards don't attack wisps, I would have died had he not decided to kill the guards there. Heh, sometimes the druids really do help more than the guards. Thanks Dolt ;) <BR>  <BR> PS: Dont use mend in combat until you're lvl20 & 1/2 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub2.ezboard.com/ushaidon.showPublicProfile>Shaidon </A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Global user</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/15/00 2:36:52 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The closest I've been to death without dying </span><hr size=1> I wanted to do this for a LONG time.=)  Now that *bumps* are fashionable, I suppose I shall do this. <BR>  <BR> *bump* <BR> *g