A bunch of elves were camping the bank in Kelethin when this poor Gnome decided to do deposit her loot.  They rooted her and all started hitting on her.  She was very patient, closed her bank account, /tapped her foot, and as soon as the root broke ran out the door and off the edge of the platform.<br>
<br>
