<br>
Then the strange part.  The entire server crashed.  When it finally goes back up she logs on and finds that her last save point was in mid-air!  So she only falls for half the distance, hits the ground, and runs off to recuperate.  No death at all.<br>
<br>
If only we could arrange these convenient all-server crashes more often.<br>
